title: New Dong Phuong Tofu
description: A vegetarian restaurant serving mostly vegan food; vegans please inquire as to the vegetarian items. Menu includes pho, curries, noodle dishes, rice dishes and more. Also offers a large array of a la carte dishes, which can also be ordered in combination with rice or white/yellow noodles. Specialty is vegan fake meats, Vietnamese style. Located in a strip mall with plenty of parking. Mostly take-out but seating is available. Quaint comfortable atmosphere.
